y faltaría calcular los extremos del polinomio 
\begin_inset Formula $g\!\left(x\right)=x\cdot\left(x-\frac{\pi}{4}\right)\cdot\left(x-\frac{3\pi}{4}\right)\cdot\left(x-\pi\right)$
