\max\!\left\{ \left|f\!\left(x\right)-P_{n}\!\left(x\right)\right|:x\in\left[-1,1\right]\right\} \le\frac{1}{2^{n}\left(n+1\right)!}\cdot\max\!\left\{ \left|f^{\left.n+1\right)}\!\left(x\right)\right|:x\in\left[-1,1\right]\right\} 
