status open

\begin_layout Definition
Llamamos 
\series bold
diferencias divididas generalizadas
\series default
 a 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f\!\left[x_{0},\dots,x_{k}\right]=\begin{cases}
\begin{array}{c}
\frac{f\left[x_{1},\dots,x_{k}\right]-f\left[x_{0},\dots,x_{k-1}\right]}{x_{k}-x_{0}}\\
\\
\frac{f^{\left.k\right)}\left(x_{0}\right)}{k!}
\end{array} & \begin{array}{c}
\begin{array}{cc}
\text{si} & x_{k}\ne x_{0}\end{array}\\
\\
\begin{array}{cc}
\text{si} & x_{k}=x_{0}\end{array}
\end{array}\end{cases}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Esta definición completa la que vimos de diferencias divididas.
